# 🎮 High Score Game in C :

## 📖 Description
This is a simple C-based game that tracks and updates the player's high score using global variables.

## 🚀 Features
- Score tracking system
- High score update logic
- Simple console-based UI

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Language: C

## 📂 How to Run
1. Compile using gcc
2. Run the executable file

## 🎯 Learning Outcome
- Understanding of global variables
- Function usage in C
- Basic game logic

